original_prompt: An ultra-realistic photograph in the style of a 1980s Vogue editorial, shot on Kodachrome film. A stunning, slender Black model with chic short hair holds a rigid, geometric, high-fashion pose. The intense lighting casts stark, hard-edged graphic shadows across the minimalist poolside patio. She wears a couture strapless mini-dress with a structured white bodice and delicate ostrich feathers. A wide, chunky diamond cuff bracelet glitters intensely on her wrist, casting small points of light. The scene is defined by deep contrast and vibrant, oversaturated colors, with blown-out specular highlights on the turquoise water and the diamonds. Full body shot, hyper-detailed, sharp focus, 16:9 aspect ratio.
